  "title": "refactor(geo): implement controlled map [PART-4]",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR revamp the GeoSearch renderer to use a \"controlled\" map. We leverage the provided `currentRefinement` to (almost) always render the map from a bounding box. It simplify a lot the workflow of the widget - we don't rely anymore on complicated conditions to init the position. This refactor also allow us to implement a proper support for the URLSync.",
